{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_06_03",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ダンス大会当日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "会場入りしたが、異様な雰囲気だな\nみんな怜を遠巻きに見るだけで、誰も近づいて来ないぞ",
      "startTime": 6.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私の出場はネットでも話題になっていましたから\n疎ましく感じてるんだと思います",
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ダンサーの立場なら、自分達のステージに\nアイドルがしゃしゃり出て、いい気はしませんよね",
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜にとっては完全にアウェーってことか……\nだが、中には怜と話したい人もいるみたいだぞ",
      "startTime": 29.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4233.333333399997,
          "startTime": 33.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ……エリカ……\n向こうも準備は出来ているみたいですね",
      "startTime": 41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri001.m4a",
      "text": "怜……よく恥ずかしげもなく顔を出せたわね",
      "startTime": 44.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "今日は決着をつけに来たわ",
      "startTime": 48.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri002.m4a",
      "text": "ふざけないで。そんなヒラヒラしたドレスで踊る気？\n自分が場違いだって分からないの？",
      "startTime": 56.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri003.m4a",
      "text": "そもそもダンスから逃げてアイドルになったあんたが\n今更大会に出たところで……",
      "startTime": 62.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "それは違うわ。私はダンスから逃げた訳じゃない",
      "startTime": 64.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "私のダンスを生かす道を考えて\nアイドルに可能性を見出しただけよ",
      "startTime": 72.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "私はダンスを捨てていない\n今日、あなたに勝ってそれを証明するわ",
      "startTime": 78.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "平島エリカ",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-hiraeri004.m4a",
      "text": "真剣にダンス一筋に打ち込んできた私が\nアイドルに負ける訳ないでしょ",
      "startTime": 85.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "いくら口で言っても納得しないでしょうね",
      "startTime": 87.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "だからパフォーマンスで、あなたが馬鹿にした\n『アイドル』の本気を思い知らせてあげる",
      "startTime": 94.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 98.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 98.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（プログラムが順調に進んで、いよいよ怜の出番だが）\n（果たしてアイドルが受け入れてもらえるのか……）",
      "startTime": 104.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 107.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "会場のみなさん、こんにちは！\nエントリーナンバー12番、一ノ瀬怜です！",
      "startTime": 111.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 115.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "今日、私はアイドルとしてここに来ました！",
      "startTime": 115.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 119.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（会場がざわついているな……。ダンス大会なのに）\n（いきなりアイドル宣言されたら困惑するのも当然か）",
      "startTime": 123.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 119.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 127.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "世の中にはいろんなダンスがあります\nどんなダンスも等しく素敵で素晴らしい……",
      "startTime": 131.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "私の……アイドルのダンスを見てそれを感じて下さい！",
      "startTime": 135.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 141.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "ここからはアイドルが輝く時間です！\nテンション上げて行きますよー！",
      "startTime": 144.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.8
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（サニピの曲にあわせて笑顔で明るく元気に踊って……）\n（怜はあくまでアイドルとして勝つつもりだな）",
      "startTime": 154.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "私と一緒に踊って楽しんで！\n最高に楽しいステージにしましょう！",
      "startTime": 160.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.33333330001,
          "startTime": 162.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（怜のアイドルを貫き通したパフォーマンスは）\n（大会で一番の盛り上がりを見せた。そして――）",
      "startTime": 166.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_danceconteststage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestage",
      "startTime": 171.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、優勝出来て嬉しいです",
      "startTime": 172.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3000,
          "startTime": 175.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（終わってみれば、怜の圧勝だった）\n（あの盛り上がりを見れば誰も文句は言えないだろう）",
      "startTime": 180.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei017.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの私がダンスの大会に出場することに\n戸惑われた方も多いと思います",
      "startTime": 188.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_06_03-rei018.m4a",
      "text": "場違いだと思った方もきっといると思います\nでも、私はみんなに知ってほしかったんです",
      "startTime": 195.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
